Name: Mistake on CS 425 Assignment
Short description: I have just realized that when I assigned HW 4 to the class, I made a few mistakes on the pdf which contains the assignment.
Content:
Mistake on HW #4.

‍

I have just realized that when I assigned HW 4 to the class, I made a few mistakes on the pdf which contains the assignment.

‍

Here was the mistake:

The ER diagram that I released for the homework had a 1:1 between table D and C, when it should have been a 1:N, and "Location_ID" should be a private key since the company that this is modeled after has so many locations for their stores that they use an ID instead of a city.

‍

Feel free is you have questions or concerns. The reason this is important is because the SQL script you have to write is supposed to make this ER diagram, and those two bits of information would change the code that you are writing.
Author: haleigh-boyle

Name: Any advice on the CS 487 Team Presentation?
Short description: Just need some quick advice on software and how to put in audio over the video
Content:
Any advice on the CS 487 Team Presentation?

Currently, I am thinking of using OBS to record my screen while I am showing the website (our final prototype) so that he can see and hear me talk while looking at the site. Just wondering what other students are using?

What I am looking for.

Any other software to use that may not be as difficult to operate, or just other methods of getting audio played over a video and lined up with a video.
Author: jerod-macejkovic
